{"type":"message","id":"dae92270","parentId":"31419138","timestamp":"2026-03-26T01:18:52.230Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There are paper trading files for 7 accounts:\n1. `paper_` (default)\n2. `paper_defensive_`\n3. `paper_balanced_`\n4. `paper_aggressive_`\n5. `paper_alpha55_`\n6. `paper_exit_dual_`\n7. `paper_exit_tight_`\n\nI need to read the order CSVs to get the proposed buy lists for each account. Let me read the orders CSV files to see what stocks are proposed for buying today.","thinkingSignature":"29316ee8d7718ff215dbb90abb646738d1101bb6a45a0d706c14804f664cdfa8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7n765xunsn24_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"for prefix in paper_defensive paper_balanced paper_aggressive paper_alpha55 paper_exit_dual paper_exit_tight paper; do\n  f=\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/${prefix}_orders_v1_20260326.csv\"\n  echo \"=== $prefix ===\"\n  if [ -f \"$f\" ]; then\n    python3 -c \"\nimport csv, sys\nwith open('$f') as fp:\n    reader = csv.DictReader(fp)\n    rows = list(reader)\n    if rows:\n        buys = [r for r in rows if r.get('action','').upper() in ('BUY','买入') or (r.get('signal','')+r.get('action','')).upper().strip() not in ('', 'SELL','卖出')]\n        print('Total rows:', len(rows), '| Cols:', list(rows[0].keys())[:8])\n        # print header\n        print('Headers:', list(rows[0].keys()))\n        # find buy rows\n        buy_rows = [r for r in rows if 'buy' in str(r).lower() or '买' in str(r).lower()]\n        print('Buy-like rows:', len(buy_rows))\n        if buy_rows:\n            print(buy_rows[0])\n    else:\n        print('EMPTY')\n\"\n  else\n    echo \"FILE NOT FOUND\"\n  fi\ndone","timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":16442,"output":441,"cacheRead":22075,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38958,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cac