state_file) as f:\n\n[394 more lines in file. Use offset=250 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774492851543}}
{"type":"message","id":"59f28621","parentId":"26ceee61","timestamp":"2026-03-26T02:41:15.873Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a good picture. The staleness check currently:\n1. Computes lag = feature_latest_date - signal_date (days)\n2. If lag > MAX_SIGNAL_LAG_DAYS (2 days), marks as stale\n\nBut this misses the case where features are also stale. I need to also compare signal_date against the current date.\n\nAlso, I want to add:\n1. A `current_date` field in the meta so the report can show \"current date vs signal date\"\n2. Better stale reason that also mentions the absolute age\n3. A `refresh_hint` that tells users how to refresh\n\nLet me also check what `generate_report()` currently shows when stale, and then fix it.\n\n\nNow I need to modify `load_latest_signals()` to add the current date comparison and refresh hint to the meta, then update `generate_report()` to display a more prominent stale warning with the signal age and instructions for refreshing.","thinkingSignature":"6ba086499527b8d6cb41d2ead15401be33d43e60450cfd04d8ddac2f21ac4c27"},{"type":"text","text":"Now I have the full picture. The stale detection is working (confirmed: `signal_stale=True`), but the report output when stale is insufficient. Let me apply the fixes:\n\n**Fix 1**: `load_latest_signals()` — add current-date-based staleness check + refresh hint\n**Fix 2**: `generate_report()` — make the stale banner much more prominent and include absolute age\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_7yljcdhwrczf_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/run_breadth_paper_trading.py","old_string":"    top_stocks = hs300.sort_values('pred_rank', ascending=False).head(topk).copy()\n    signal_date = latest_date.date().isoformat()\n    feature_latest_date = load_feature_latest_date()\n    signal_lag_days = None\n    stale_reason = \"\"\n    is_stale = False\n    if feature_latest_date:\n        lag_days = (datetime.strptime(feature_latest_date, \"%Y-%m-%d\").date() - latest_date.date()).days\n        signal_lag_days = max(lag_days, 0)\n        if lag_days > MAX_SIGNAL_LAG_DAYS:\n            is_stale = True\n            stale_reason = f\"信号已过期：预测文件最新日期 {signal_date}，但特征数据已到 {feature_latest_date}，落后 {lag_days} 天\"\n\n    meta = {\n        \"prediction_path\": str(prediction_path),\n        \"signal_date\": signal_date,\n        \"feature_latest_date\": feature_latest_date,\n        \"signal_lag_days\": signal_lag_days,\n        \"is_stale\": is_stale,\n        \"stale_reason\": stale_reason,\n        \"preferred_live_predictions\": str(LIVE_PREDICTIONS_PATH),\n    }\n    return signal_date, top_stocks, meta","new_string":"    top_stocks = hs300.sort_values('pred_rank', ascending=False).head(topk).copy()\n    signal_date = latest_date.date().isoformat()\n    feature_latest_date = load_feature_latest_date()\n    current_date = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d\")\n    signal_lag_days = None\n    absolute_lag_days = None\n    stale_reason = \"\"\n    is_stale = False\n    # Check 1: signal vs feature (relative staleness)\n    if feature_latest_date:\n        lag_days = (datetime.strptime(feature_latest_date, \"%Y-%m-%d\").date() - latest_date.date()).days\n        signal_lag_days = max(lag_days, 0)\n        if lag_days > MAX_SIGNAL_LAG_DAYS:\n            is_stale = True\n            stale_reason = f\"信号已过期：预测文件最新日期 {signal_date}，但特征数据已到 {feature_latest_date}，落后 {lag_days} 天\"\n    # Check 2: signal vs today (absolute staleness — catches case where both feature and signal are old)\n    abs_lag = (datetime.strptime(current_date, \"%Y-%m-%d\").date() - latest_date.date()).days\n    absolute_lag_days = max(abs_lag, 0)\n    if absolute_lag_days > MAX_SIGNAL_LAG_DAYS:\n        is_stale = True\n        if stale_reason:\n            stale_reason += f\"；另：信号距今已实际过期 {absolute_lag_days} 天（当前日期 {current_date}）\"\n        else:\n            stale_reason = f\"信号已过期：预测文件最新日期 {signal_date}，距今已 {absolute_lag_days} 天未刷新（当前日期 {current_date}），超过阈值 {MAX_SIGNAL_LAG_DAYS} 天\"\n    refresh_hint = (\n        f\"提示：预测文件路径 {str(prediction_path)}；\"\n        f\"LIVE预测文件路径 {str(LIVE_PREDICTIONS_PATH)}（不存在）；\"\n        f\"需运行 Qlib 每日特征/预测更新流程，或手动刷新 ml_predictions.csv 到最新交易日后重试。\"\n    ) if is_stale else \"\"\n\n    meta = {\n        \"prediction_path\": str(prediction_path),\n        \"signal_date\": signal_date,\n        \"feature_latest_date\": feature_latest_date,\n        \"current_date\": current_date,\n        \"signal_lag_days\": signal_lag_days,\n        \"absolute_lag_days\": absolute_lag_days,\n        \"is_stale\": is_stale,\n        \"stale_reason\": stale_reason,\n        \"refresh_hint\": refresh_hint,\n        \"preferred_live_predictions\": str(LIVE_PREDICTIONS_PATH),\n        \"live_predictions_exist\": LIVE_PREDICTIONS_PATH.exists(),\n    }\n    return signal_date, top_stocks, meta"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":45338,"output":1218,"cacheRead":22075,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68631,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774492851555,"responseId":"0613cfb324a9620fe142929635cc517c"}}
