号过期 — 交易已暂停（自动调仓冻结）</div>\"\n            f\"<div class='stale-grid'>\"\n            f\"<div><span class='lbl'>信号日期</span><span class='val'>{signal_date}</span></div>\"\n            f\"<div><span class='lbl'>当前日期</span><span class='val'>{current_date}</span></div>\"\n            f\"<div><span class='lbl'>信号绝对过期</span><span class='val warn'>{abs_lag} 天</span></div>\"\n            f\"<div><span class='lbl'>特征数据最新</span><span class='val'>{feat_date}</span></div>\"\n            f\"<div><span class='lbl'>预测文件</span><span class='val mono'>{pred_file}</span></div>\"\n            f\"<div><span class='lbl'>LIVE预测</span><span class='val'>{'✅ 存在' if live_exists else '❌ 不存在'}</span></div>\"\n            f\"<div><span class='lbl'>执行状态</span><span class='val'>{exec_status}</span></div>\"\n            f\"</div>\"\n            f\"<div class='stale-reason'>原因：{metrics.get('signal_stale_reason') or '预测信号未刷新，超出允许阈值'}</div>\"\n            f\"<div class='stale-action'>刷新指引：{refresh_hint if refresh_hint else '需运行 Qlib 每日特征/预测更新流程，刷新 ml_predictions.csv 后重试。'}</div>\"\n            f\"</div></article>\"\n        )"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":50089,"output":760,"cacheRead":22075,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72924,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774492918396,"responseId":"0613cff66d15ada54e864442a5ef5cf6"}}
