{"type":"message","id":"78f3730d","parentId":"f0e74559","timestamp":"2026-03-26T02:46:22.541Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Git commit succeeded. The commit hash is `3f272cf`. Now let me update the ACTIVE_TASK.md to mark the current task as done and update the next steps.\n\nThe task was:\n- Current: 修改 breadth_aggressive 执行链：增加信号过期检测、过期状态输出，并预留 live 信号刷新入口。\n- Next: 重跑宽度盘脚本与面板，验证过期状态已显式暴露；提交 git 记录并向张玲回传验收件。\n\nBoth are now done. Let me update the ACTIVE_TASK.md.","thinkingSignature":"e95527d50227fc7c60307a96bc37e04721d1022e8a96b5fbee081cae1bb1ca9e"},{"type":"text","text":"Git commit `3f272cf` confirmed. Now update `ACTIVE_TASK.md`:\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_aowhsp15oqog_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md","content":"Status: done\nPriority: P1\nStarted: 2026-03-26 10:38\nUpdated: 2026-03-26 10:50\nWorkspace: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\nOwner: main-session\n\n## Goal\n- 修复 breadth_aggressive 宽度盘静默复用旧信号的问题，避免 2026-03-03 旧信号在后续日期继续被当作\"最新交易信号\"执行与展示。\n\n## Acceptance\n- 代码层阻断旧信号静默复用：当信号文件日期明显落后于特征/数据最新日期时，宽度盘不能再默默沿用旧信号继续交易。\n- 报表/面板能明确展示\"信号已过期/需刷新\"，而不是让用户误以为系统仍在正常滚动交易。\n- 至少完成一轮本地验证，并给出涉及文件路径、命令输出与 git 提交证据。\n\n## Current\n- 无（任务已完成）\n\n## Next\n- 无（后续由独立任务补充 Qlib 每日特征/预测自动刷新流程）\n\n## Completed\n- [2026-03-26 10:38] 确认检测逻辑现状：signal_stale=True / signal_stale_reason 已正确设置 / execution_status=signal_stale_hold\n- [2026-03-26 10:43] 增强 load_latest_signals()：新增绝对过期检测（signal_date vs current_date），新增 absolute_lag_days / current_date / refresh_hint / live_predictions_exist 字段\n- [2026-03-26 10:45] 增强 generate_report()：过期时输出独立表格（信号日期/当前日期/绝对过期天数/特征日期/预测文件/LIVE预测/执行状态），替换原来单行 blockquote\n- [2026-03-26 10:47] 增强 generate_breadth_aggressive_dashboard()：compute_metrics() 新增字段暴露；HTML stale banner 升级为红色渐变卡片，含图标、6项检查网格、原因说明、刷新指引\n- [2026-03-26 10:50] 完成本地验证并提交 git：commit 3f272cf\n\n## Evidence\n- `run_breadth_paper_trading.py` 中 `load_latest_signals()` 输出：\n  [WARN] 信号已过期：预测文件最新日期 2026-03-03，但特征数据已到 2026-03-10，落后 7 天；另：信号距今已实际过期 23 天（当前日期 2026-03-26）\n- `generate_report()` 输出含 `🚨 信号过期 — 交易已暂停` 二级标题及专格\n- `breadth_aggressive_paper_latest.json` 含 `absolute_lag_days: 23`, `current_date: 2026-03-26`, `refresh_hint` 非空\n- `breadth_aggressive_dashboard_latest.html` 含 `信号过期 — 交易已暂停` banner\n- git commit: `3f272cf`\n\n## Blockers\n- ML 预测管道未自动滚动（ml_predictions.csv 最新 2026-03-03）：属于下一阶段自动刷新任务，本次已通过增强展示做到了\"显式暴露\"；刷新流程本身由后续任务补全\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":89750,"output":867,"cacheRead":22075,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112692,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774493161937,"responseId":"0613d0ea56499058406ce1ede44bb0e4"}}
