{"type":"message","id":"d1a4a3f9","parentId":"8b6a8551","timestamp":"2026-03-26T02:46:34.449Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me send the completion report to the user (张玲). The task is now complete. Let me provide a concise summary of what was done.","thinkingSignature":"611020ae523bedcc95b6baa1e94a4d6d653cee95dadb67519265bff2407871d6"},{"type":"text","text":"**修复完成 ✅**\n\n---\n\n**问题确认**：宽度盘检测逻辑本身已正确（`signal_stale=True`），但展示层对\"交易已冻结\"表达不充分，导致用户可能误以为系统正常运行。\n\n**本次改动**（2 个文件，`3f272cf`）：\n\n1. **`run_breadth_paper_trading.py` — `load_latest_signals()`**\n   - 新增**绝对过期检测**（`signal_date` vs `current_date`），解决\"特征和预测同时旧\"时旧信号被静默使用的问题\n   - 新增字段：`absolute_lag_days`（23天）、`current_date`、`refresh_hint`、`live_predictions_exist`\n\n2. **`run_breadth_paper_trading.py` — `generate_report()`**\n   - 过期时输出独立二级标题 `🚨 信号过期 — 交易已暂停` + 6项检查表格（信号日期/当前日期/绝对过期天数/特征日期/预测文件/LIVE预测存在性）\n   - 不再是原来模糊的单行 blockquote\n\n3. **`generate_breadth_aggressive_dashboard.py`**\n   - HTML banner 升级为红色渐变背景卡片，含图标、6项检查网格、原因说明、刷新操作指引\n\n**验证输出**：\n```\n[WARN] 信号已过期：预测文件最新日期 2026-03-03，但特征数据已到 2026-03-10，落后 7 天；\n       另：信号距今已实际过期 23 天（当前日期 2026-03-26）\nsignal_stale=True | absolute_lag_days=23 | execution_status=signal_stale_hold\n```\n\n**遗留**：ML 预测管道本身（`ml_predictions.csv` 停在 03-03）需单独修复，属于下一阶段任务。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":90655,"output":419,"cacheRead":22075,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113149,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774493182672,"responseId":"0613d0fe7661bb35951acd4b9cd9dd4d"}}
