{"type":"message","id":"89635dea","parentId":"eaf910d0","timestamp":"2026-03-26T14:02:46.332Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, both compile. Now generate the audit report.","thinkingSignature":"4468afcec28a6346bc8132f3678948fd00efb552b95f14255f90de0d07542d3b"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5uosymojzb3o_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/research/reports/中文化检查_20260326.md","content":"# 用户可见输出中文化检查报告\n**日期**：2026-03-26\n**检查范围**：workspace/scripts/ 与 quant_projects/ 下直接发给张玲的生成/推送脚本\n\n---\n\n## 一、已发现并修复的问题\n\n### 1. `generate_investment_research_chief_broadcast.py`\n**问题**：广播消息中对 `overall_status`、`freshness.status`、`health.status`、`ths.status`、`bq.status` 等字段直接展示原始英文值（如 \"PASS\"、\"ALERT\"、\"fresh\"、\"stale\"、\"unknown\"）。\n\n**修复**：\n- 新增 `cn_status()` 函数（与 `chief_card.py` 映射同步）\n- 替换 3 处 raw status 引用：\n  - `paper_freshness.status` → `cn_status(paper_freshness.status)`\n  - `hp.status` → `cn_status(hp.status)`\n  - `ths.status` → `cn_status(ths.status)`\n  - `sa.overall_status` → `cn_status(sa.overall_status)`\n  - `bq.status` → `cn_status(bq.status)`\n\n**修改文件**：`scripts/generate_investment_research_chief_broadcast.py`\n\n---\n\n### 2. `generate_live_global_dashboard.py`\n**问题**：实盘指挥面板 HTML 中，盘前强检状态显示原始 \"PASS\" / \"ALERT\" 英文。\n\n**修复**：\n- 将 `precheck_status` 变量重命名为 `precheck_status_cn`\n- 值从 `\"PASS\"` → `\"通过\"`，`\"ALERT\"` → `\"告警\"`\n- HTML 模板中相应引用改为 `{precheck_status_cn}`\n\n**修改文件**：`quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/generate_live_global_dashboard.py`\n\n---\n\n## 二、扫描范围（已确认为安全）\n\n| 脚本 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| `push_investment_research_paper_execution.py` | ✅ 中文主内容；delivery status 字段为内部 JSON，不直接展示 |\n| `push_breadth_strict_oos_alert_if_needed.py` | ✅ 无英文暴露 |\n| `push_control_tower_alert_if_changed.py` | ✅ 无英文暴露 |\n| `generate_investment_research_chief_card.py` | ✅ 已有完整 `cn_status()` 映射 |\n| `generate_investment_research_control_tower.py` | ✅ 英文仅存于内部映射字典，不直接展示 |\n| `generate_investment_research_control_tower_card.py` | ✅ 英文仅存于内部映射字典，不直接展示 |\n| `generate_investment_research_control_tower_broadcast.py` | ✅ 英文仅存于内部映射字典，不直接展示 |\n| `generate_investment_research_mainline_health.py` | ✅ 已用 `cn_status()`；alert_message 使用中文 |\n| `sync_ths_exports.py` | ✅ 无英文暴露 |\n| `push_morning_news_broadcast.py` | ✅ 无英文暴露 |\n\n---\n\n## 三、后续建议\n\n1. **持续监控**：新引入推送/面板脚本时，默认检查 status 相关字段是否通过 `cn_status()` 映射\n2. **规则写入规范**：在 `AGENTS.md` 或 `TOOLS.md` 中固化\"所有用户可见 status 字段必须过 cn_status 映射\"规则\n3. **中文标签**：面板/报告中的字段名（如 \"PRECHECK\"、\"AUDIO\"）也逐步替换为中文标签，当前优先级较低\n\n---\n\n## 四、修改证据\n\n```\ngit diff --stat HEAD~1 scripts/generate_investment_research_chief_broadcast.py\ngit diff --stat HEAD scripts/generate_live_global_dashboard.py\n```\n\n**验证命令**：\n```bash\npython3 -m py_compile scripts/generate_investment_research_chief_broadcast.py\npython3 -m py_compile quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/generate_live_global_dashboard.py\n```\n两者均输出 OK，无语法错误。\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43969,"output":912,"cacheRead":22075,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":66956,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774533742634,"responseId":"06146f6e9741d8e1a1f6e5704aaffa6c"}}
